definitions.text:
[đỏ mặt] to blush; to flush; to crimson; to be red in the face 
 Đỏ mặt vì giận dữ 
 To crimson with fury; 
 To be apoplectic with fury; 
 To be red with anger 
 Đỏ mặt vì ngượng 
 To blush with shame; 
 To be red with shame

